short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make Unipd.it great again. Was it ever great tho?

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A neat little extension that modifies the look of parts of Unipd.it and it's pages.

If you ever opened the login page at Unipd.it and thought "Ugh, this thing is ugly af..." then this extension is for you.

As of today (Jan 26 2022), the extension only replaces the interface of the department of engineering login page and it's navigation bar.
long.it:
